<p><a name="History" id="History"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Persian_Empire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: History">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">History</span></h2>
<p><a name="Median_Persian_Empire_.28728_BC-559_BC.29" id="Median_Persian_Empire_.28728_BC-559_BC.29"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Persian_Empire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Median Persian Empire (728 BC-559 BC)">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Median Persian Empire (728 BC-559 BC)</span></h3>
<div class="rellink noprint relarticle mainarticle">Main article: <a href="/wiki/Medes" title="Medes">Medes</a></div>
<table class="infobox" style="background: none; border: none; width: 290px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4em; margin-right:0;">
<tr>
<td>
<table class="infobox geography vcard vevent" style="width:290px;">
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="mergedtoprow fn org summary" align="center" style="line-height:1.2em; font-size:135%;"><b>Median Empire</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="vertical-align:middle; text-align:center; border-top: solid 1px #aaa; padding: 0.2em 0em 0.2em 0em; background:#EFEFEF">
<table width="100%" style="text-align:center; margin:0 auto; background:none;">
<tr>
<td width="50px" style="border:0; vertical-align:middle; font-size:30%; line-height: 105%;"><a href="/wiki/Neo-Assyrian_Empire" title="Neo-Assyrian Empire"><span style="font-size:300%;">←</span></a> <a href="/wiki/File:Blank.png" class="image" title="Blank.png"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d2/Blank.png" width="30" height="20" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a><br /></td>
<td style="vertical-align:middle; text-align:center; font-size:115%; border:0"><b>728 BC&#160;–&#160;559 BC</b></td>
<td width="50px" style="border:0; vertical-align: middle; text-align:right; line-height: 105%; font-size:30%;"><a href="/wiki/File:Blank.png" class="image" title="Blank.png"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d2/Blank.png" width="30" height="20" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Achaemenid_Empire" title="Achaemenid Empire"><span style="font-size:300%;">→</span></a><br /></td>
