<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.iranica.com/newsite/index.isc?Article=http://www.iranica.com/newsite/articles/unicode/v4f6/v4f6a015.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.iranica.com/newsite/index.isc?Article=http://www.iranica.com/newsite/articles/unicode/v4f6/v4f6a015.html" rel="nofollow">[2]</a></li>
