<li id="cite_note-17"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://india_resource.tripod.com/Europetrade.html" class="external text" title="http://india_resource.tripod.com/Europetrade.html" rel="nofollow">"European Domination of the Indian Ocean Trade"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://india_resource.tripod.com/Europetrade.html" class="external free" title="http://india_resource.tripod.com/Europetrade.html" rel="nofollow">http://india_resource.tripod.com/Europetrade.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-01-10</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=European+Domination+of+the+Indian+Ocean+Trade&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Findia_resource.tripod.com%2FEuropetrade.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Persian_Empire"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
